CHANGES
------------------------------

[ 2008-03-18 / version 1.1 ]
Added capability to additionally copy file to a destination, locally or
remotely, via ssh. This can be in addition to or instead of mailing.
Now one must specify -m for mailing, and -c for copying

[ 2008-02-28 / version 1.0 ]
Initial version to send mail with attachments from the command line
